## Setup

Set the target API base URL:

```bash
export OPENCLI_BASE_URL='http://127.0.0.1:8000'
```

## Body Input

Simple JSON body endpoints accept top-level flags plus raw JSON input modes:

```bash
./bin/{{ .App.Name }} auth login --email you@example.com --password secret --remember
./bin/{{ .App.Name }} auth login --data '{"email":"you@example.com","password":"secret","remember":true}'
./bin/{{ .App.Name }} auth login --file login.json
```

## Trace

Enable HTTP request and response tracing with:

```bash
./bin/{{ .App.Name }} --trace auth login --email you@example.com --password secret --remember
```

